/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `nhds -/
theorem tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto_top_dual_pairing {l : filter α} {f : α → weak_dual 𝕜 E} {x : weak_dual 𝕜 E} :
    tendsto f l ((nhds) x) ↔
      ∀ y, tendsto (fun i => top_dual_pairing 𝕜 E (f i) y) l ((nhds) (top_dual_pairing 𝕜 E x y)) :=
  weak_bilin.tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto _ continuous_linear_map.coe_injective
#align tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto_top_dual_pairing tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto_top_dual_pairing
tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `nhds -/
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `nhds -/
theorem tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto {l : filter α} {f : α → weak_bilin B} {x : weak_bilin B}
    (hB : function.injective B) : tendsto f l ((nhds) x) ↔ ∀ y, tendsto (fun i => B (f i) y) l ((nhds) (B x y)) := by
  rw [← tendsto_pi_nhds, embedding.tendsto_nhds_iff (embedding hB)]
#align tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto tendsto_iff_forall_eval_tendsto

eval_continuous:
theorem eval_continuous (y : E) : continuous fun x : weak_dual 𝕜 E => x y :=
  continuous_pi_iff.mp coe_fn_continuous y
#align eval_continuous eval_continuous
embedding:

/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr →ₗ[ ] » -/
/-- The coercion `(λ x y, B x y) : E → (F → 𝕜)` is an embedding. -/
theorem embedding {B : «expr →ₗ[ ] » E 𝕜 («expr →ₗ[ ] » F 𝕜 𝕜)} (hB : function.injective B) :
    embedding fun (x : weak_bilin B) y => B x y :=
  function.injective.embedding_induced <| linear_map.coe_injective.comp hB
#align embedding embedding
